39 1536w" width="384" height="512" alt="Finding strength and embracing self-care in Manchester - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Finding strength and embracing self-care in Manchester - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-ilfuhL fjsXRa pf-55_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-71e2" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-lkgTHX jrzygT pf-56_"><div style="--cw:800px" class="sc-fmBCVi iwpzju"><div class="sc-kfPuZi ihOOoE pf-57_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXEqDS hwCMhq pf-58_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brSvTw kXcmVH pf-59_">Finding strength and embracing self-care
